\begin_layout Itemize
Asian cycad scale, 
\emph on
Aulacaspis yasumatsui
\emph default
, detected in 2003 on ornamental plants
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Infestation quickly spread to wild plants.
 By 2006, 
\emph on
C.
 micronesica
\emph default
 was placed on the IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
To date, 90% of Guam's 
\emph on
